<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Account Status Update - {{companyName}}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; {{#if isActive}}background: #d4edda; border-bottom: 3px solid #28a745;{{else}}background: #f8d7da; border-bottom: 3px solid #dc3545;{{/if}} }
    .content { padding: 24px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .status-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px; {{#if isActive}}background: #d4edda; color: #155724;{{else}}background: #f8d7da; color: #721c24;{{/if}} }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h2 style="margin: 0;">Account Status Updated</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
    <p>Your account status for <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> has been updated.</p>
    
    <p><strong>New Status:</strong> <span class="status-badge">{{#if isActive}}Active{{else}}Inactive{{/if}}</span></p>
    <p><strong>Updated By:</strong> {{updatedBy}}</p>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> {{updatedAt}}</p>

    {{#if isActive}}
      <p>You now have access to the portal based on your assigned role (<strong>{{roleName}}</strong>). You can log in at any time using your existing credentials.</p>
      <p style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #0066cc; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">Log In Now</a>
      </p>
    {{else}}
      <p>Your access to the portal has been temporarily suspended. You will not be able to log in or access company resources until your status is reactivated by an administrator.</p>
      <p>If you believe this is an error, please contact your administrator: {{adminEmail}}</p>
    {{/if}}

    <p><strong>Role:</strong> {{roleName}}</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This notification was sent to {{email}} regarding your account at {{companyName}}.</p>
    <p>© {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>